## Identity Operators
'''
- It will check whether left value is equal to
 the right value or not

"python" is "Python" 
'''

print(1 is 1) # O/P = True

print(2 is 1)  # O/P = False

print("python" is "Python") # O/P = False

print(1 is 0) # O/P = False

print(1 is not 1) # O/P = False

print("hi hello"  is not  "hello hi") # O/P = True

